{"lastModified":1774635025249,"uri":"c::7580644256::vessel::08a9c1a0-696d-11f0-ad9d-07b9f506a1a7","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Step aboard SUMMER SUNSET, your private escape to the beauty of the Pacific Northwest. Recently refit in 2025, this 92' Tarrab motor yacht blends timeless style with modern comfort — the perfect setting to unwind, explore, and create unforgettable memories. \n \nWith four spacious cabins accommodating eight guests, SUMMER SUNSET feels like your own floating sanctuary. Wake up to serene views and enjoy coffee on the aft deck. Spend your day kayaking through quiet coves, paddleboarding on calm waters, or fishing from the swim platform as eagles soar overhead. The inflatable swim deck adds extra space for sunbathing or simply soaking in the stunning scenery. \n \nEvery journey aboard SUMMER SUNSET is tailored to you. Whether you’re seeking adventure or peaceful relaxation, this yacht charter delivers an unparalleled experience. Let the natural beauty of the Pacific Northwest set the stage while SUMMER SUNSET becomes your home on the water. ","blueprint":{"name":"SUMMER SUNSET","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::08a9c1a0-696d-11f0-ad9d-07b9f506a1a7::assets::6e929f50-e000-11f0-adc6-ff6606098771/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::08a9c1a0-696d-11f0-ad9d-07b9f506a1a7::assets::6e8ecec1-e000-11f0-aee2-0bffcbab110e/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::08a9c1a0-696d-11f0-ad9d-07b9f506a1a7::assets::6e8ea7b0-e000-11f0-aee3-0bffcbab110e/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::08a9c1a0-696d-11f0-ad9d-07b9f506a1a7::assets::6e8d6f30-e000-11f0-aee1-0bffcbab110e/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::08a9c1a0-696d-11f0-ad9d-07b9f506a1a7::assets::6e8e0b70-e000-11f0-aee2-0bffcbab110e/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::08a9c1a0-696d-11f0-ad9d-07b9f506a1a7::assets::6e8d9640-e000-11f0-aee1-0bffcbab110e/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::08a9c1a0-696d-11f0-ad9d-07b9f506a1a7::ass